data.description: Cute country 1268 sq ft 2/1 home with family room with garage and work space. Along with a 1/1 apartment.Both have updated kitchens and floors. This property has a lot to offer from privacy, garden, ponds and so much more. Timber on upper side of  property. Main home and apartment has separate drive ways. Several out buildings and fenced garden. Apartment has potential for rental income. Flat Lot with lots of potential.
